snippet.title: Teaser Trailer丨Super Sus Official Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Available NOW on both GooglePlay and AppStore!!
Are you ready for the new level of Super Sus!?
Download NOW on
GooglePlay: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.je.supersus
AppStore: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/super-sus/id1595589498
TapTap: https://www.taptap.io/app/224386

Features:
1. Find the impostors, Settle in 7 minutes.
2. 20+ unique roles. Play as you wish.
3. Multiple modes, Rank to top & beyond!
4. Built-in Voice Chat. Make new friends pain-free.
5. Team up & Play with anyone in any country!
